1. Loadstone
Keeps all customer info in one place.
Makes it easy to follow up with leads.
Helps teams work together smoothly.

2. Salesforce
Popular and powerful CRM.
Automates sales and marketing tasks.
Gives smart insights to improve sales.

3. Oracle Customer Experience (CX)
Connects sales, marketing, and support in one system.
Personalizes customer experience using AI.
Tracks customer interactions across channels.

4. HubSpot
Easy to use, even for beginners.
Helps manage contacts and email campaigns.
Shows simple dashboards to track progress.

5. AmoCRM
Great for small businesses.
Lets you chat with customers inside the CRM.
Automatically organizes sales pipelines and tasks.
